{"tid":1768221,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"萊坊：預計香港優質街鋪租金將錄得2013年以來最大跌幅","createTime":"2019-12-04T02:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T12:53:39.000Z","uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0332ab798e5921e68349487c24c443d3da763a","tid":1768221,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"【彭博】-- 萊坊表示，2020年香港主要購物區的租金將急劇下跌，因示威活動持續，香港的零售銷售萎縮幅度創紀錄。<br />\n萊坊的高級總監Helen Mak表示，來年中環、銅鑼灣、尖沙咀和旺角等地區的街鋪租金將下降15%或以上，為2013年以來最大跌幅。Mak表示，對於外國和本地租戶而言，在決定現在是否開設門店時當然不得不保持謹慎，這會拖累租金。<br />\n如果上述預估兌現，街鋪租金下降可能削弱香港作為全球最昂貴的零售物業租賃市場的地位。高緯環球稱，儘管自6月份開始爆發示威活動，但第三季度銅鑼灣街鋪的租金仍為全球最高，達每年每平方呎2,544美元。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：高緯環球<br />\n原文標題<br />\nHong Kong to See Biggest Fall in Prime Retail Rents since 2013<br />\n欲聯繫記者請洽：Shawna Kwan Hong Kong wkwan35@bloomberg.net<br />\n欲聯繫英文編輯請洽：Katrina Nicholas knicholas2@bloomberg.net, Marcus Wright<br />\nFor more articles like this, please visit us at <a href=\"http://bloomberg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbloomberg.com&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=e8dbf904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a><br />\n&copy;2019 Bloomberg L.P.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/money/news/萊坊預計香港優質街鋪租金將錄得2013年以來最大跌幅/ar-BBXJ0sg?li=AAazejl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fmoney%2Fnews%2F%E8%90%8A%E5%9D%8A%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%84%AA%E8%B3%AA%E8%A1%97%E9%8B%AA%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E5%B0%87%E9%8C%84%E5%BE%972013%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C%E5%B9%85%2Far-BBXJ0sg%3Fli%3DAAazejl&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=0f222aa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/money/news/萊坊預計香港優質街鋪租金將錄得2013年以來最大跌幅/ar-BBXJ0sg?li=AAazejl</a>"},{"pid":"b99aa4187926884bbf29871995fb421a196f5477","tid":1768221,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T02:29:54.000Z","msg":"維吾爾人權政策法過左！上twitter 賀一